1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:01,800
加工海鲜怎么收费啊
How much do you charge for seafood processing?

2
00:00:01,800 --> 00:00:03,399
一个元的几块
A few yuan per person.

3
00:00:03,399 --> 00:00:04,400
一个元头的
Per head.

4
00:00:04,400 --> 00:00:06,280
你们会不会换海鲜啊
Will you swap our fresh seafood for something else?

5
00:00:06,280 --> 00:00:07,480
会
Yes, we will.

6
00:00:07,480 --> 00:00:10,040
今天在广州南沙逛海鲜市场
Today we are exploring the seafood market in Nansha, Guangzhou.

7
00:00:10,040 --> 00:00:11,400
看看仨人要花多少
Let's see how much it costs for the three of us.

8
00:00:13,919 --> 00:00:15,919
这季节正好是珠江口
It's the perfect season at the Pearl River Estuary.

9
00:00:15,919 --> 00:00:17,400
很多海鲜肥美的时候
A time when a lot of seafood is plump and delicious.

10
00:00:18,679 --> 00:00:19,960
海鲜都在哪啊
Where is the seafood?

11
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,000
在这
Over here.

12
00:00:21,000 --> 00:00:21,600
哦
Oh.

13
00:00:22,800 --> 00:00:23,600
要不要
Do you want some?

14
00:00:23,600 --> 00:00:24,400
三千的
These are 3,000.

15
00:00:24,400 --> 00:00:25,800
这个是多少钱啊
How much is this?

16
00:00:25,800 --> 00:00:26,920
五十块一块
50 yuan per piece.

17
00:00:26,920 --> 00:00:28,039
有十二个的
There are twelve in total.

18
00:00:28,039 --> 00:00:30,199
一块钱一只的是哪个呀
Which one is 1 yuan per piece?

19
00:00:30,199 --> 00:00:31,640
一块钱到点套餐一起买的
The 1 yuan ones are part of a combo set.

20
00:00:31,640 --> 00:00:32,879
这三个线有什么
What's in this three-item set?

21
00:00:32,879 --> 00:00:33,879
单买就是一百五
It's 150 if bought separately.

22
00:00:33,879 --> 00:00:35,200
然后加起来就是一百
But together it's only 100.

23
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,200
还要一斤多
And more than a catty extra.

24
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:36,960
多酥鸭
Duck with crispy skin.

25
00:00:36,960 --> 00:00:38,039
还要那个白贝呀
And those white clams.

26
00:00:38,039 --> 00:00:38,799
海草啊
Seaweed too.

27
00:00:38,799 --> 00:00:39,679
全部鲜活的
All fresh and alive.

28
00:00:40,679 --> 00:00:42,200
我总觉得哪里不对
I feel like something is not quite right.

29
00:00:43,200 --> 00:00:45,799
你是不是把它标的高一点单买
Did you mark the single price higher on purpose?

30
00:00:45,799 --> 00:00:47,719
这样显得套餐便宜一点
To make the combo set look cheaper?

31
00:00:47,719 --> 00:00:48,920
对 没错
Yes, exactly.

32
00:00:49,480 --> 00:00:51,079
我是不是揭露你了
Did I just expose you?

33
00:00:51,079 --> 00:00:52,439
啊 没事没事
Ah, it's fine, no problem.

34
00:00:52,439 --> 00:00:53,239
不是很正常
Isn't that normal?

35
00:00:53,239 --> 00:00:54,359
来一百块钱吧
Let's get 100 yuan worth.

36
00:00:54,359 --> 00:00:55,320
这样很好啊
This is very good.

37
00:00:55,320 --> 00:00:57,519
带着不用撑就不是说嫌带着重
Easy to carry, not heavy at all.

38
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,440
很会做生意 再逛一下
You're good at business. Let's look around more.

39
00:00:59,720 --> 00:01:01,560
酱麻棒15块钱一个
Snail sticks are 15 yuan each.

40
00:01:01,560 --> 00:01:02,560
能摸吗
Can I touch them?

41
00:01:02,560 --> 00:01:04,480
可以 关注你很久了
Sure, I've been following you for a long time.

42
00:01:04,480 --> 00:01:06,200
所以那你肯定不会坑我是不是
So you definitely won't rip me off, right?

43
00:01:06,200 --> 00:01:06,799
是啊
Of course not.

44
00:01:08,600 --> 00:01:09,680
这个都是我的
These are all mine.

45
00:01:09,680 --> 00:01:11,200
你帮我挑4个吧
Help me pick four.

46
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,000
60块
That's 60 yuan.

47
00:01:12,000 --> 00:01:12,439
好
Okay.

48
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:13,600
50块卖不卖啊
Will you sell them for 50?

49
00:01:13,600 --> 00:01:14,040
可以
Okay.

50
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:14,920
那40呢
What about 40?

51
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,400
那你上视频你就完蛋了
If you're in the video, you're doomed.

52
00:01:18,400 --> 00:01:20,040
坏死你啊告诉你
I'm telling you, you'll be in trouble.

53
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:22,120
我就砍10块
I'm only bargaining for 10 yuan.

54
00:01:22,120 --> 00:01:22,920
50块啊
50 yuan, then.

55
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:23,439
好
Okay.

56
00:01:23,439 --> 00:01:25,920
我想买炒虾那些有吗
Do you have those stir-fried shrimps?

57
00:01:25,920 --> 00:01:26,800
我看看
Let me see.

58
00:01:26,799 --> 00:01:28,799
这个桥下就是天涯的
These shrimps are top quality.

59
00:01:28,799 --> 00:01:30,000
我懂天涯
I know quality when I see it.

60
00:01:30,000 --> 00:01:30,799
多少钱啊
How much are they?

61
00:01:30,799 --> 00:01:32,000
75块
75 yuan.

62
00:01:32,000 --> 00:01:33,399
买衣服应该多不多啊
Should we buy more?

63
00:01:33,399 --> 00:01:34,000
不可以
No, that's enough.

64
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,799
你们这袋子都挺厚的啊
Your bags are quite thick.

65
00:01:35,799 --> 00:01:38,200
我捶的一块钱袋子还在那边攒
I'm still saving that 1-yuan bag I bought.

66
00:01:38,200 --> 00:01:39,200
哈哈哈哈
Hahaha.

67
00:01:39,200 --> 00:01:40,000
18块
18 yuan.

68
00:01:40,000 --> 00:01:40,599
好
Okay.

69
00:01:40,599 --> 00:01:41,799
黄角丽有没有啊
Do you have yellowfin sea bream?

70
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,799
你去她的
Go to her stall.

71
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,000
四眼才能见到
Only professionals can spot them.

72
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,799
诶
Hey.

73
00:01:44,799 --> 00:01:45,599
刘雨昕
Liu Yuxin!

74
00:01:45,599 --> 00:01:46,599
诶 你好你好
Hey, hello, hello.

75
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:48,599
看来今天不用怕被坑了
Looks like I don't have to worry about being ripped off today.

76
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,799
黄角丽在前面并有
There's yellowfin sea bream up ahead.

77
00:01:49,799 --> 00:01:50,799
我带你去吗
Shall I take you there?

78
00:01:50,799 --> 00:01:52,799
这个是正宗古地的黄角丽
This is authentic local yellowfin sea bream.

79
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:54,000
当时都是半两半年生
They're all about six months old.

80
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,200
来 两条吧
Let's get two.

81
00:01:55,200 --> 00:01:56,000
38块的
38 yuan.

82
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,480
他们默认出了个袋子的
They usually include a bag.

83
00:01:57,480 --> 00:01:59,079
这边还有什么本地的
What other local specialties are here?

84
00:01:59,079 --> 00:01:59,959
要不搞定这个
How about this one?

85
00:01:59,959 --> 00:02:00,879
控肥鱼
Fatty fish.

86
00:02:00,879 --> 00:02:02,599
现在是最好吃最肥的时候
Now is when they're the fattiest and most delicious.

87
00:02:02,599 --> 00:02:03,560
这个35
This one is 35.

88
00:02:03,560 --> 00:02:04,280
来一点
Get some.

89
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,239
18块
18 yuan.

90
00:02:05,239 --> 00:02:06,960
你们这边人好多互相帮助啊
People here are so helpful to each other.

91
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:08,639
没事 都是邻居
It's nothing, we're all neighbors.

92
00:02:08,639 --> 00:02:09,879
有那种水蟹吗
Do you have those water crabs?

93
00:02:09,879 --> 00:02:10,639
我帮你拿
I'll get them for you.

94
00:02:10,639 --> 00:02:11,840
他生意都不做了
He's not even attending to his own business.

95
00:02:11,840 --> 00:02:12,719
人太好了
He's such a nice person.

96
00:02:12,719 --> 00:02:13,680
哎 刘萍萍
Hey, Liu Pingping!

97
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,920
哎 哈喽哈喽
Hey, hello, hello.

98
00:02:14,920 --> 00:02:15,920
水蟹没有肉
Water crabs have no meat.

99
00:02:15,920 --> 00:02:16,840
就吸那个汁
You just suck the juices out.

100
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,360
对对对
Yes, exactly.

101
00:02:17,360 --> 00:02:18,120
来 三个吧
Let's get three.

102
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,039
三个
Three.

103
00:02:19,039 --> 00:02:21,000
就本地的海鲜都差不多了
The local seafood is mostly like this.

104
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,240
好像没在你店里买的
It seems I didn't buy anything from your stall.

105
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:22,840
没所谓的
It doesn't matter.

106
00:02:22,840 --> 00:02:23,879
谢谢
Thank you.

107
00:02:23,879 --> 00:02:25,479
这个叫黄蜜桃
This is called 'Yellow Peach' (local seafood name).

108
00:02:25,479 --> 00:02:26,359
这个本地有
We have it locally.

109
00:02:26,359 --> 00:02:27,280
15一斤
15 yuan per catty.

110
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,439
70块给你
I'll give it to you for 70.

111
00:02:28,439 --> 00:02:29,039
来一点
Get some.

112
00:02:29,039 --> 00:02:29,879
28
28 yuan.

113
00:02:29,879 --> 00:02:32,519
你本人比照片好看很多
You look much better in person than in photos.

114
00:02:32,519 --> 00:02:33,759
起码年轻10岁
At least ten years younger.

115
00:02:33,759 --> 00:02:34,519
谢谢
Thank you.

116
00:02:34,519 --> 00:02:36,479
哇 这个好东西
Wow, this is good stuff.

117
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:38,159
省蟑螂 比较浓湿
Very rich and flavorful.

118
00:02:38,159 --> 00:02:38,919
这多少钱
How much is this?

119
00:02:38,919 --> 00:02:39,680
28一斤
28 yuan per catty.

120
00:02:39,680 --> 00:02:40,680
这么便宜
So cheap!

121
00:02:40,680 --> 00:02:41,479
一两
Per tael (50g).

122
00:02:41,479 --> 00:02:41,960
啊 一两
Oh, per tael.

123
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,039
200块一斤
That's 200 yuan per catty.

124
00:02:43,519 --> 00:02:44,519
我们这边的配方就是
Our recipe here is...

125
00:02:44,519 --> 00:02:46,039
如果月料非常多
If there are a lot of ingredients...

126
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,280
就是可以用来包它
We can use them to wrap it.

127
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:48,280
快点来一点吧
Let's get some quickly.

128
00:02:48,280 --> 00:02:49,039
90块
90 yuan.

129
00:02:49,039 --> 00:02:50,039
122元
122 yuan.

130
00:02:50,039 --> 00:02:51,039
谢谢
Thank you.

131
00:02:51,039 --> 00:02:53,159
买了这么多一共是420
We bought so much, total is 420 yuan.

132
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:55,840
我们找了一个离市场有点距离的地方加工
We found a place a bit further from the market for processing.

133
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,599
加工海鲜怎么收费啊
How much for seafood processing?

134
00:02:57,599 --> 00:03:00,199
一个人10块 给人头的
10 yuan per person, per head.

135
00:03:01,039 --> 00:03:02,400
包括什么做法呢
What cooking methods are included?

136
00:03:02,400 --> 00:03:05,120
蒸 白炒 煎 加烧 10块
Steaming, stir-frying, pan-frying, all for 10 yuan.

137
00:03:05,120 --> 00:03:06,800
炸 干 洗五
Deep-frying, drying, and cleaning.

138
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:08,199
把它投餐就两块
Just 2 yuan extra for the set.

139
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,400
哦 这个虾
Oh, these shrimps.

140
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:10,039
这个白炒
Stir-fry these.

141
00:03:10,039 --> 00:03:11,319
那不用额外花钱了
Then no extra money needed.

142
00:03:11,319 --> 00:03:12,639
这个是水蟹
These are water crabs.

143
00:03:12,639 --> 00:03:13,280
草啊
Seaweed.

144
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,319
做粥可不可以啊
Can we make congee with these?

145
00:03:14,319 --> 00:03:15,039
不做啊
No, we don't.

146
00:03:15,039 --> 00:03:16,000
哈哈哈哈
Hahaha.

147
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:17,000
这个蒸的可以
These can be steamed.

148
00:03:17,000 --> 00:03:17,719
黄角粒啊
Yellowfin sea bream.

149
00:03:17,719 --> 00:03:19,400
蒸 拿这个生蒸
Steam these fresh.

150
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,439
拿这个生蒸
Steam these fresh.

151
00:03:20,439 --> 00:03:21,439
这个排骨
These ribs.

152
00:03:21,439 --> 00:03:24,479
你这买多少都是按人头收
No matter how much you buy, it's per head.

153
00:03:24,479 --> 00:03:26,560
你们会不会换海鲜啊
Will you swap our fresh seafood?

154
00:03:26,560 --> 00:03:29,159
嘿 我们这面20年了
Hey, we've been here for 20 years.

155
00:03:29,159 --> 00:03:30,120
我的面海鲜
Our seafood is authentic.

156
00:03:32,840 --> 00:03:33,719
这就夫妻店
This is a mom-and-pop shop.

157
00:03:33,719 --> 00:03:35,039
就叔叔阿姨两个人
Just the uncle and aunt running it.

158
00:03:39,919 --> 00:03:42,120
白灼的炒虾蘸点酱油
Boiled shrimps dipped in soy sauce.

159
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,879
真的很甜
It's really sweet.

160
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:46,680
皮很薄
The skin is very thin.

161
00:03:46,680 --> 00:03:48,599
本店说这个是叉王
The shop says these are top tier.
